      "text": "WESTLUND, Jacqueline Kory and BREAZEAL, Cynthia, 2015. The Interplay of Robot Language Level with Children’s Language Learning during [[Storytelling]]. In: Proceedings of the Tenth Annual ACM/IEEE International Conference on Human-Robot Interaction Extended Abstracts. Online. Portland Oregon USA: ACM. 2 March 2015. p. 65–66. ISBN 978-1-4503-3318-4. DOI 10.1145/2701973.2701989. [Accessed 30 November 2023]."
